7.17.4.1 The atomic_thread_fence function
Synopsis
1

#include <stdatomic.h>
void atomic_thread_fence(memory_order order);
Description

2

Depending on the value of order, this operation:
— has no effects, if order == memory_order_relaxed;
278

Library

